FACET is a Framework for Aspect Composition of an EvenT Channel. You
can find more information on the web at :

http://www.cse.wustl.edu/~doc/RandD/PCES/facet/

For instructions on building and installing FACET, please see the
INSTALL file. 

FACET is made up of a number of different features. Please see the
doc/ directory for some documentation on the architecture of FACET,
its features as well as tips on how you can write your own feature.

The NEWS file contains information on what has changed between
releases as well as some other announcements of relevance.

For examples on how to use FACET in a variety of scenarios, please see
the examples/ directory. 

